{"directed": true, "multigraph": false, "graph": {}, "nodes": [{"node_type": "DOCUMENT", "label": "Acme Master Data Policy v1", "doc_type": "policy", "department": "Compliance Department", "date": "2024-01-01", "summary": "The document establishes Acme's Master Data Policy, outlining core rules for handling user data. It mandates encryption with AES-256 and limits data retention to three years, and lists the entities involved such as Project Titan and CloudStorage Pro.", "status": "indexed", "id": "4d7310fe-3f2a-4a67-989a-77bb612561cf"}, {"node_type": "DOCUMENT", "label": "Project Titan Implementation Guide", "doc_type": "policy", "department": "Engineering Department", "date": null, "summary": "The document provides an implementation guide for Project Titan, detailing how to apply the Acme Master Data Policy v2 with quantum\u2011safe encryption across all databases. It also outlines updates to the CloudStorage Pro API, including automatic log deletion after one year, and references integration with AWS KMS.", "status": "indexed", "id": "5585fdfd-62b6-4fc8-8750-2ed2f2804ff2"}, {"node_type": "DOCUMENT", "label": "Security Audit Report 2026", "doc_type": "compliance", "department": "Security Operations", "date": null, "summary": "The Security Audit Report 2026, authored by Security Operations, highlights a critical finding that the integration with AWS KMS is failing. This vulnerability blocks the Project Titan Implementation Guide from moving to production, posing a significant security risk.", "status": "indexed", "id": "9b274203-022e-482f-aecb-8f0325399ba2"}, {"node_type": "DOCUMENT", "label": "Acme Master Data Policy v2", "doc_type": "policy", "department": null, "date": "2026-01-01", "summary": "The Acme Master Data Policy v2 establishes core rules for handling user data, requiring quantum\u2011safe encryption and limiting retention to one year. It supersedes the previous version and lists entities such as Project Titan and CloudStorage Pro that are subject to th